data.name: UsaAverageHouseholdSizeOverlayInfo

data.name: UsaDiversityIndexOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI thematic map provides racial and ethnic diversity in the United States.

data.name: UsaRailNetworkOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI overlay map provides railway system in the United States. The data set, from the Federal Railroad Administration (FRA) rail network database, provides location and attribute information for use in national and regional network analysis applications.

data.name: UsaRetailSpendingPotentialOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI thematic map provides the Spending Potential Index (SPI) for retail goods in the United States in 2010

data.name: UsaSocialVulnerabilityOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI thematic map provides a simple summary of the social vulnerability of populations in each state or county in the United States in 2009

data.name: UsaSoilSurveyOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI overlay map provides the Soil Survey Geographic (SSURGO) by the United States Department of Agriculture’s Natural Resources Conservation Service.

data.name: UsaUnemploymentRateOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI thematic map provides the unemployment rates in the United States in 2010

data.name: WorldAdministrativeOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI overlay map provides administrative boundaries, cities, water features, physiographic features, parks, landmarks, highways, roads, railways, airports.

data.name: WorldBoundariesDarkOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI overlay map provides country, state, province, and county or equivalent boundaries and names of place for the World. It appears best when overlaying on dark basemaps

data.name: WorldBoundariesLightOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI overlay map provides country, state, province, county or equivalent boundaries and names of place for the World. It appears best when overlaying on light basemaps.

data.name: WorldDeLormesMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap provides a DeLorme’s topographic map with seamless global data set that portrays transportation, hydrography, jurisdiction boundaries, and major geographic features.

data.name: WorldImageryMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap provides satellite imagery for the World and high resolution imagery for the United States and other areas around the World.

data.name: WorldLightGrayMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap draws attention to your thematic content by providing a neutral background with minimal colors, labels, and features.

data.name: WorldLightGrayOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI overlay map provides labels for selected cities and towns around the World, in support of the WorldLight Gray basemap.

data.name: WorldNationalGeographicMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap provides a general reference map for informational and educational purposes as well as a basemap by GIS professionals and other users for creating web maps and web mapping applications.

data.name: WorldOceansMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap provides bathymetry, surface and subsurface feature names, and derived depths. This map layer is designed to be used as a basemap by marine GIS professionals and as a reference map by anyone interested in ocean data.

data.name: WorldPhysicalMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap provides the Natural Earth physical map for the World.

data.name: WorldShadedReliefMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap provides surface elevation as shaded relief. It is intended for use as a basemap layer to add shaded relief to other GIS maps.

data.name: WorldStreetMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap provides highway level data for the World and street level data for North America, Europe, Southern Africa, parts of Asia, and more.

data.name: WorldTerrainMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap provides shaded relief imagery, bathymetry, and coastal water features designed to provide a neutral background for other data layers.

data.name: WorldTopographicMapInfo
data.value: This ESRI basemap is a World topographic map with boundaries, cities, water features, physiographic features, parks, landmarks, transportation, and buildings.

data.name: WorldTransportationOverlayInfo
data.value: This ESRI overlay map provides a transportation and street name labels reference overlay that is particularly useful on top of imagery.
